{"tid":2354692,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"美服巨商 The Great Merchant 新一年新開始 #10","createTime":"2021-01-05T15:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T03:17:41.000Z","uid":59060,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfe30077ce953a869eae47d1cfcb2042344e4a8","tid":2354692,"uid":59060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"巨商呢隻GAME 唔洗多介紹啦<br />\n由爛橙到普雷威 都十年有多 仲要受代理無限CAP水抽封書?<br />\n想完夢? 想合神? 合天王? 美服幫到你<br />\n想輕鬆玩? 課金玩? 想點玩都得<br />\n我地人數唔多但凝聚力強及親民，經常交流玩法，歡迎想入坑又唔知點入手<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://www.thegreatmerchant.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegreatmerchant.com%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=466bb204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thegreatmerchant.com/</a><br />\n商團: Kongner<br />\n本團Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/DPRv2kQbSr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FDPRv2kQbSr&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=19ea345e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/DPRv2kQbSr</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時版本為明朝冥王，詳情請看52巨商網。<br />\n<br />\n1.新手難唔難起手?<br />\n我哋有好多唔同風格的高手提供意見及解答新手問題，只要加入商團及有恆心玩，好快就起到手<br />\n<br />\n2.如何加入商團?<br />\n請先入Discord並留言，獲批後去Singlong申請入團，申請完後請通知管理員。<br />\n<br />\n3.點品貴唔貴? 封書又幾錢?<br />\n點品 USD 5= 5000GP = 封書封珠，市價約300m(GP格價與市場需求而變動, 課金前請三思)，有時候節日會出特價<br />\n<br />\n4.想要巨錢快速起手應該點做?<br />\n建議課金換巨錢保障安全(防止因空交易外掛錢被永久封鎖，而曾經有不少案例發生過)，當中以封書封珠性價比最高<br />\n<br />\n5.多唔多外掛?<br />\n美服外掛唔算多(未影響到市場)，GM以前捉掛手法令人喪膽，換咗新GM之後就ON99<br />\n<br />\n6.美巨以咩人流為主?<br />\n主要以印尼, 台灣, 香港, 中國等等<br />\n<br />\n7.合神合馬難唔難?<br />\n本團內有大量廠主可以借廠消牌，合神冇難度，更有大量升LV變態佬，有時間會同大家組隊升/吸升兵<br />\n<br />\n如想問詳細資料，歡迎加入Discord頻道一齊吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，歡迎新手一齊入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61252615068ee742dffd8d20e886d04d0a894582","tid":2354692,"uid":214686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f975a2a1c0511aa21f729db6be5f7a5c0d310b5","tid":2354692,"uid":328079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"推到1001"},{"pid":"65e80a68d354cb75247f8233cafb5f0c53b51e67","tid":2354692,"uid":15562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fad00e7508f25c55618d1bf8558182deabf74d","tid":2354692,"uid":54604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc77916515d58ebce4d15bf91f8e8b1981ac89c4","tid":2354692,"uid":59060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239d24a6c6c3e06278c6683c87dca82b4543f58d","tid":2354692,"uid":214686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ad7cd534388bf3f32d363f18219638079d7e12","tid":2354692,"uid":15562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2580dc25b8d970782027519567e0fa7566f8e2","tid":2354692,"uid":140335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:48:35.000Z","msg":"留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現加wfh緊"},{"pid":"caef39c49ffc55cee460a408411f4685b1a7995c","tid":2354692,"uid":140335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img 